Garen seems to be completely bugged in Ultra Rapid Fire this year. His E - Judgement, is able to stack and do double damage. This is incredibly broken and seriously needs to be fixed. Riot **NEEDS** to think of this as a bug fix and **NOT ** an U.R.F balance that should be ignored since URF is a &quot;Bonus game mode&quot;.

Please fix this 

-Salty Urf player.   {{champion:86}}   {{champion:86}} {{item:3070}}
